Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Brother President Abu-'Ammar [Yasir 'Arafat] 
received this afternoon the ambassador of the People's Republic 
of China in Tunis. Brother President Abu-'Ammar informed the 
Chinese ambassador about the content of the talks held recently 
in Tunis with the Israeli delegation and also about the content 
of the talks held with the U.S. and Russian envoys regarding the 
necessity of implementing Security Council Resolution 904 and 
particularly ensuring the international protection of our 
Palestinian people in the occupied territories. 
  Brother President Abu-'Ammar asked the Chinese ambassador to 
urge the Chinese leadership to exert efforts with all the 
concerned parties to implement the resolution rapidly. 

